/-!
# Dirichlet characters
This file defines Dirichlet characters over (ℤ/nℤ)* and then relates them
to multiplicative homomorphisms over ℤ/nℤ for any n divisible by the conductor.

## Main definitions
 * `dirichlet_character`
 * `asso_dirichlet_character`
